Onboarding notes
----------------

  --kv-channels 128                            HF has explicit head_dim=128;
                                               hidden 3136 / heads 40 does not
                                               divide evenly.
  --untie-embeddings-and-output-weights        HF tie_word_embeddings=False.
  --attention-backend auto                     flash path was briefly suspected
                                               during debug; keep auto for now.
  no --recompute-granularity/method needed     4B fits on TP=2 H200 easily.
  EVAL_ARGS cleared                            avoids 'eval_datasets required
                                               when eval_interval set'.

The runner script parks on the TP=2 x PP=2 cell. Flip the PERF_ARGS block +
OUT_DIR suffix to rerun a specific cell.
